  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575650/extras/c2df3e97d672868fededf2d88212a227.avif?t=1644768291\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>Eric is a prince. Lately, his mother urges him to get married.<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with several dating events and endings, featuring Live2D animation system.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> become a king!<br></li><li> attack another country!<br></li><li> end the war!<br></li><li> forget about everything and run away with your maid!</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (All character routes. Also it depends on your reading speed).",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575650/extras/c2df3e97d672868fededf2d88212a227.avif?t=1644768291\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>Eric is a prince. Lately, his mother urges him to get married.<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with several dating events and endings, featuring Live2D animation system.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> become a king!<br></li><li> attack another country!<br></li><li> end the war!<br></li><li> forget about everything and run away with your maid!</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (All character routes. Also it depends on your reading speed).",
